{"questionId":"11ee667b-8898-4917-b74e-33237205e2ef_20","correctAnswer":"4","section":"Math","steps":[{"title":"Apply the simplification from the given condition","content":"Combine: $8(2-7x)+6 = 7(2-7x)+2$, giving $(2-7x)=-4$."},{"title":"Compute the target value","content":"So $7x-2 = -(2-7x) = 4$. The answer is <strong>4</strong>."}]}